Package: flocast
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, python3 (>= 3.10), python3-wxgtk4.0, python3-numpy, python3-serial, python3-pil, python3-certifi, python3-urllib3, python3-pip, libsndfile1, gir1.2-appindicator3-0.1
Description: Configure and control FlooGoo USB Bluetooth dongles
 FlooCast is a desktop application for configuring FlooGoo USB Bluetooth
 dongles (FMA120). It supports pairing with Bluetooth headsets and speakers,
 audio streaming, VoIP calls, and AuraCast broadcast functionality.
